video: use flag to not avoid small resolution HW acceleration

crrev/c/2798965 landed a new flag to not avoid using HW
acceleration on VA-API DUTs. This CL adds it to the already
existing one for allowing HW acceleration on small
resolutions.

BUG=b:179459055
TEST=video.Play.vp9_hw on samus passing.

